    (comment 1 "USB-C PD → AITRIP → XL4015 (5.1V) → ESP32-D + PCA9685 + VEML7700")
    (comment 2 "Two I2C buses: servo (GPIO21/22) + sensor (GPIO25/26)")
    (comment 3 "PCA9685 drives 4× MG90D servos via CH0–CH3")
    (comment 4 "Build: breadboard prototype with hand-wired connections")
