  (text "\n════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\nLOADS\n════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════" (at 50 250 0) (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5) (thickness 0.2)) (justify left)))

  (text "ESP32-D (WROOM-32D DevKit)\n\nConnections:\n  • VIN ← V5_OUT\n  • GND ← GND\n  • GPIO21 (SDA) ← I2C servo bus\n  • GPIO22 (SCL) ← I2C servo bus\n  • GPIO25 (SDA) ← I2C sensor bus (VEML7700)\n  • GPIO26 (SCL) ← I2C sensor bus (VEML7700)\n\nDecoupling: 100nF cap across VIN–GND\nPlacement: center of breadboard" (at 50 290 0) (effects (font (size 1 1) (thickness 0.1)) (justify left)))

  (text "PCA9685 16-Channel Servo Driver\nI2C address: 0x40 (default)\n\nConnections:\n  • V+ ← V5_OUT (via bulk cap)\n  • GND ← GND\n  • SDA ← GPIO21 (from ESP32)\n  • SCL ← GPIO22 (from ESP32)\n  • CH0–CH3 → MG90D servo signals\n\nBulk capacitor: 1000–2200 µF ≥10V\nPlacement: close to V+ pin\nDecoupling: 100nF cap across V+–GND" (at 350 290 0) (effects (font (size 1 1) (thickness 0.1)) (justify left)))

  (text "VEML7700 Light Sensor\nI2C address: 0x10 (default)\n\nConnections:\n  • VDD ← V5_OUT\n  • GND ← GND\n  • SDA ← GPIO25 (from ESP32)\n  • SCL ← GPIO26 (from ESP32)\n\nPlacement: mounted near window/exterior\nDecoupling: 100nF cap across VDD–GND" (at 50 550 0) (effects (font (size 1 1) (thickness 0.1)) (justify left)))

  (text "MG90D Servo × 4\n(one per shutter)\n\nConnections per servo:\n  • Red (power) ← V5_OUT servo rail\n  • Black (GND) ← GND servo rail\n  • Yellow (signal) ← PCA9685 CH0/CH1/CH2/CH3\n\nNote: Stagger servo startup in firmware\nto limit inrush current" (at 350 550 0) (effects (font (size 1 1) (thickness 0.1)) (justify left)))

  (text "\n════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\nCRITICAL WIRING NOTES\n════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════" (at 50 750 0) (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5) (thickness 0.2)) (justify left)))

  (text "① SET XL4015 OUTPUT VOLTAGE TO EXACTLY 5.1V WITH A MULTIMETER BEFORE CONNECTING LOADS" (at 60 790 0) (effects (font (size 1 1) (thickness 0.15)) (bold)) (justify left)))

  (text "② I2C Pull-up Resistors: 4.7kΩ on each I2C bus\n   Servo bus (GPIO21/22): 4.7kΩ to V5_OUT\n   Sensor bus (GPIO25/26): 4.7kΩ to V5_OUT" (at 60 810 0) (effects (font (size 1 1) (thickness 0.1)) (justify left)))

  (text "③ Servo Rail Bulk Capacitor: 1000–2200 µF (≥10V rated)\n   Connect between PCA9685 V+ and GND\n   Place as close as physically possible to PCA9685 V+ pins" (at 60 830 0) (effects (font (size 1 1) (thickness 0.1)) (justify left)))

  (text "④ Decoupling: 100nF capacitors across VDD–GND for:\n   • ESP32-D\n   • PCA9685\n   • VEML7700" (at 60 850 0) (effects (font (size 1 1) (thickness 0.1)) (justify left)))

  (text "⑤ Common Ground: Single-point star ground at XL4015 GND output\n   All return paths converge here (ESP32, PCA9685, VEML7700, servo GND)" (at 60 870 0) (effects (font (size 1 1) (thickness 0.1)) (justify left)))

  (text "⑥ Servo Power Rail: Wide copper/wiring (1–2mm) from capacitor to servo connectors\n   Must supply 2–3A peak without voltage drop" (at 60 890 0) (effects (font (size 1 1) (thickness 0.1)) (justify left)))

  (text "⑦ Firmware: Stagger MG90D startup to prevent inrush current spike\n   Do not drive all servos simultaneously at power-on" (at 60 910 0) (effects (font (size 1 1) (thickness 0.15)) (justify left)))

)
